      "type": "text",
      "title": "The Logotype",
      "text": "The logo and all graphic elements are based on one question: how do we show SaaShok’s main value – connection? We created a special symbol called the \"Link.\" By connecting two unique parts, this shape became the main graphic element and the foundation of the brand.",
      "variant": "dark",
      "padding": "compact"
    },
    {
      "type": "media",
      "padding": "default",
      "files": ["../../assets/projects/saashok/5.jpg"]
